{"tid":1844624,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"野狼陳偉霆春晚再掀高潮：不要忘記永遠是中國人","createTime":"2020-01-26T17:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T02:17:12.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"381a083a24fb386d050e1686545b9aab2c47fec7","tid":1844624,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-01-26-18-05-01F0N49ZNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-01-26-18-05-01F0N49ZNs.jpg&h=553de9d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男歌手陳偉霆近因神曲《野狼Disco》而備受關注，想不到一個月後再有新演出！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-01-26-18-05-31mXuxksJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-01-26-18-05-31mXuxksJg.jpg&h=0c4c31f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，央視新春節目《2020央視春節晚會》改為錄播。陳偉霆與張藝興、寶石Gem一同合唱新年版《鼠年Disco》，並以歌曲向正與肺炎疫症搏鬥的醫護人員致敬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-01-26-18-05-31fFXUfojx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-01-26-18-05-31fFXUfojx.jpg&h=dc31823e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歌曲結尾更由三人一齊合唱「時時刻刻必要要提醒你自己，一定不要忘記，無論走到那裡，你永遠都是中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/entertainment/player?newsId=378197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378197&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=a83a608e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378197&h=193f5859\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/entertainment/player?newsId=378197</a>"},{"pid":"8e32eabc7d3be7d66fcb982736ea10f4b0d28347","tid":1844624,"uid":95520,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T